{"tid":1229824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我倡議酒樓餐廳發動長輩圖網絡戰","createTime":"2019-06-16T04:48:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T04:56:37.000Z","uid":259442,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bbf24f1dbb0d9494b1b7df958e45093cd8bd1220","tid":1229824,"uid":259442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T04:48:36.000Z","msg":"今日父親節，個個都會去飲茶食飯做孝子<br />\n講真，今日會出黎遊行嘅長輩已經目標明確<br />\n但我地要target嘅係仲未覺醒嘅老一輩<br />\n運用餐廳，酒樓人流密集，將長輩圖擴散開去<br />\n<br />\n不論Airdrop, 或者用佢地電話發whatsapp,微信都得。<br />\n<br />\n在此廣集各位巴絲貼出長輩圖，好好利用今日，將連登長輩圖發揚光大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d0PULay.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd0PULay.png&h=f33882c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fm6skJU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFm6skJU.png&h=3b2e960b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fad8421b28f24852930c7fe5d471422b78df583d","tid":1229824,"uid":186152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T04:50:21.000Z","msg":"同埋無手機remote 轉撚走啲垃圾cctvb台"},{"pid":"2700fd8b06649845cbd9a735a3ea50ac0942d71d","tid":1229824,"uid":186152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T04:50:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋用手機remote 轉撚走啲垃圾cctvb台</blockquote>"},{"pid":"563b8eb636635a728b24d9e5df817e37eb8edb67","tid":1229824,"uid":143834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T04:51:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a5f5e00f6e1caabeb009d776d5de399f381f03e6","tid":1229824,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2700fd8b06649845cbd9a735a3ea50ac0942d71d","tid":1229824,"uid":186152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T04:50:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋用手機remote 轉撚走啲垃圾cctvb台</blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T04:56:37.000Z","msg":"有紅外線嘅電話裝app都可以轉"}]}